data.description: 3  bedroom, 2 bath home located in Sunset South. Convenient location to downtown the beaches. Property offers semi updated eat-in kitchen, friendly layout and two car garage. Home does need TLC. Sold AS IS. Sale subject to NCGS Chapter 1, Article 29A - 10 day upset bid. Attorney drafted addendum required. Seller makes no representation to fixtures or systems. Seller will not establish utilities for inspection (if not already on). 10 Day upset bid to begin upon the conclusion of any DD period.
